text:
Highlights for me:

1. The rest of the members never watched them practice on purpose so they can contain the excitement for the actual performance ♡
2. Gosh, BSS's energy in on another level for real! 
3. Joshua. I just miss him so much, so seeing him here made my heart really happy! (´｡• ◡ •｡`) ♡
4. Lee Chan. DiNOW of KPOP. Just watch his parts again. They're all so proud of they maknae. (+ c'mon, debuting an inside joke/sketch character at and awards show on live TV?! That in and of itself is legendary!)
5. MinWon crumbs ~
6. DK's kindness towards everyone. He is, indeed, sunshine and kindness personified. 

Just gave me a bunch of reasons to love them even more. It was a hard day as usual, but watching this (or anything Seventeen atp, really) is comforting for me.
